{"tid":1428824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【即日焦點】消息：北京研判須大規模拘捕、加快檢控以嚴刑「平暴止亂」","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:54:58.000Z","uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"318c84a8dac04db95f03149f9d7f28e207883f4f","tid":1428824,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358300&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358300%26refer%3DShare&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=5a7ba62f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358300%26refer%3DShare&h=7c21935b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358300&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】即日新聞焦點：<br />\n<br />\n【顏色革命？】消息：北京研判須大規模拘捕、加快檢控 以嚴刑「平暴止亂」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2019-08-07-18-15-07RdxD5AIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2019-08-07-18-15-07RdxD5AIE.jpg&h=ee2f0147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張曉明在深圳座談會上指，近日示威有顏色革命特徵，認為即使出動解放軍亦不會牴觸一國兩制。消息指，中央研判約有1000名極端暴力分子，背後有外國勢力在金錢及技術上支持，認為要盡快平暴止亂，警方必須進行大規模拘捕，律政司亦要加快檢控，以嚴刑阻嚇暴力升級。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【方仲賢被捕】警方：檢獲雷射槍屬高能量 浸大師生集會聯署譴責濫捕<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2019-08-07-18-13-06oc4ZsN0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2019-08-07-18-13-06oc4ZsN0w.jpg&h=1eff5dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n浸大學生會會長方仲賢購買觀星筆被捕，警方指搜獲的是高能量雷射槍，可令警員受傷，又指雖然警方不清楚方仲賢有何企圖，但他被截查時反應可疑，因此拘捕他。浸大師生則聯署和舉行集會，譴責警方無理拘捕。"},{"pid":"470baa53c569229819da6fc9655c911e4e7f10f7","tid":1428824,"uid":221237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:10:55.000Z","msg":"游擊 游擊 游擊"},{"pid":"